description: Welcome to the epitome of luxury living at EchelonSeaport. This 2 bed 2.5 bath east-facing, corner unit offers unparalleled sophistication and breathtaking views of the harbor and beyond, creating a truly remarkable living experience. The open concept kitchen/dining area is a culinary haven for everyday cooking and entertaining guests, featuring Thermador appliances, a gas cooktop and Italian cabinetry. This home boasts custom built-ins throughout, meticulously designed to maximize storage space; automatic shades and window treatments to provide effortless privacy; luxurious custom closets; and a spa-like marble bath. Your own private balcony is the ultimate private respite, where you can savor a morning coffee or unwind after a long day. Residents of Echelon enjoy elite services such as 24/7 concierge, valet garage parking, access to indoor and outdoor pools, state of the art fitness facility and more. This is an incredible opportunity to own a piece of Boston's waterfront elegance.
